Package Request

package Request
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    EventRequest
    Used when requesting a single Event associated with the current User
    FamilyEventRequest
    Used when requesting all Events for every member of the current User's tree
    FamilyRequest
    Used when requesting all Persons for every member of the current User's tree
    FillRequest
    Used to fill in a tree of 'Persons' for the current 'User'
    LoadRequest
    Used to load the provided 'User', 'Person', and 'Event' data into the database
    LoginRequest
    Used when requesting a login for the specified username and password
    PersonRequest
    Used when requesting a single Person associated with the current User
    RegisterRequest
    Used when registering a new User
